<bibRefCitation author="Burtt, B. L." box="[790,983,1113,1139]" pageId="10" pageNumber="59" pagination="81 - 109" refId="ref7592" refString="Burtt, B. L. (2001) Flora of Thailand: annotated checklist of Gesneriaceae. Thai Forest Bulletin (Botany) 29: 81 - 109." type="journal article" year="2001">Burtt (2001: 86)</bibRefCitation>
