<subSubSection pageId="10" pageNumber="59" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1436,1035,1255]" pageId="10" pageNumber="59">
Notes:—Molecular data are lacking for this species, the transfer is 
<emphasis box="[1026,1073,1152,1177]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="59">fide</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Burtt, B. L." box="[1084,1246,1152,1178]" pageId="10" pageNumber="59" pagination="81 - 109" refId="ref7592" refString="Burtt, B. L. (2001) Flora of Thailand: annotated checklist of Gesneriaceae. Thai Forest Bulletin (Botany) 29: 81 - 109." type="journal article" year="2001">Burtt (2001)</bibRefCitation>
, who included 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pellegrin" authorityYear="1926" box="[151,400,1191,1216]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Gesneriaceae" genus="Didymocarpus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="10" pageNumber="59" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="bonii">
<emphasis box="[151,400,1191,1216]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="59">Didymocarpus bonii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<taxonomicName authority="C.Y.Wu, 1982" authorityName="C. Y. Wu ex Li" authorityYear="1982" box="[441,611,1191,1216]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Gesneriaceae" genus="Calcareoboea" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="10" pageNumber="59" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[441,611,1191,1216]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="59">Calcareoboea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a second species and predicted (correctly) that also 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hemsley" authorityYear="1890" box="[1288,1406,1191,1216]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Gesneriaceae" genus="Didymocarpus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="10" pageNumber="59" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hancei">
<emphasis box="[1288,1406,1191,1216]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="59">D. hancei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is closely allied to 
<taxonomicName authority="C.Y.Wu, 1982" authorityName="C. Y. Wu ex Li" authorityYear="1982" box="[344,509,1229,1254]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Gesneriaceae" genus="Calcareoboea" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="10" pageNumber="59" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[344,509,1229,1254]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="59">Calcareoboea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Nevertheless, confirmation is needed.
</paragraph>
